-height: 1.4;"&gt; 2025 年 5 月在莫斯科举行的胜利日阅兵。&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4; font-style: italic;"&gt;资料来源：法新社/盖蒂图片社&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;国会主要共和党人&lt;/strong&gt;准备与特朗普决裂，将五角大楼的预算提高 44%，达到 1.5 万亿美元，这是&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/BTPERJnzuK8X4BfzJMPA5VVSayI22MR8DZe1IWRCWD9vq9g7YT7lK7RtjqD_n3laAK3prqQYp8mCysc0g_11G65znKIu_CKzyt_BrfhYCtBczliprgKmR5XfQ7fpd_fq2IlbP4Qff5BjMYykZz83JPwLp0u8mCg_6hG0hbqC8IamYrsQeJKBB-nQHyym80w07R1whRnQU5JxI-F7k_h9CTSN0qW_dNKHmvQh11RvklD8JRmZ3RQXRWo21e3C6GC0OljK5B90Y2VBd3zUNN0cr3jaqE7ZKUtrXnMVCbpv94GoswnkA7Q2AZye_REPUuvVK6UOehhA2ilMjUIhJyk-_PNwbvelNO8W9RRdldMy-rcZD2EF40IlptHwSPRnbUCLCcD7CYawVYjf_VH7HCVf3vE_JbZ7LTcdKlqM006N-mnqQVd_vYty77zvKoHdZX1N5_eX2fXKp54qA8MpNWNCieng1T0s9XZ9jgfbhaeq0EdgfwuJsotdg6omh7KnGsn07ZbS9D6W4ut5BPgUU-Aw4NrlrKbpVfkiSFsasZZU60pZPA/tdnKsHJbR1av-dNLliBV94qIjjLFVah-/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="特朗普 1.5 万亿美元的国防计划罕见地遭到共和党的抵制"&gt;罕见的反抗行为&lt;/a&gt;，表明随着中期选举的临近，总统的控制力正在减弱。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;将瑞士人口限制在 1000 万的提案&lt;/strong&gt;在第一次民意调查中获得了 52% 受访者的支持，显示&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/Ia1uvX7_GJ18Hu_JLxxFcjdIEbwT9yAAK4YIc1SxZhMtEb5I9MBYJL1O8_f5Xrg7FoG8lBj0ViCL7-zNReogWc1LEOUtcwCQidS47-Mxn86ztAc7019bbm4Kn2XZ5Rm9ROy5FTKzcPITWR1SAGWebw3kZp3m43swkl6jtKmM1rl4A5rd-5doYs-UeCfP9kYr1FzwOM5CWaQV8YG4oXhJfS-fjRnfuwnfWr3AJA1QvrwFF_hD2bVGZvwfDGAhYyAJlPZXiz3_u1W-w9Bw2ftCJ1jFAC4gqozJf0O3KE9D2KTZUHOiLO88FbjJGx95R2bc-gWDOg1ojljitSb5Ki_kjGgbundv8VLBnxGDGmu4ODPn7vZT8ytW99aLrML649tspOrKemYQ0QDk9_3AkgyyJy9CTZ-twKw2Fm2AEV5uE_kDz9GQvfeRKQPkpGmsR_bkvKxjzy1k5NV09G6Wwty7ouO0cvoqAVEHaDncsVx8R21GXAA2TAmq-hcq-SbE7-ZYSKMUC91LTyMdalamrHikZsYCBjrtnPvFVc-Y7yauiGQ/6IofgEu-cJoTqaJK5oJpnVOy8YV7P7tO/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-siz